  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5992047/" class="title-link">时代精神的精华</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5992047"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/46976702/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/46976702/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">缙云野人</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-05-26"
      class="main-meta">2013-05-26 21:12:12</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5992047_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  读了之后，感慨颇多。回首历史，西学东渐百年来，出了数十位哲人，为民族振兴寻找理论道路。然而，真正的融汇东西哲学的人，陈嘉映先生是第一个！陈嘉映先生的哲学将是中华民族复兴的精神支柱！我们为中国有这样的学者而庆幸！天不生嘉映，万古如长夜！

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 1没用</span>
